title: This is how Kylie Jenner tricked everyone with fake ‘boob surgery’
text:
Other Articles SC dismisses ONGC plea to reconsider arbitration venue Snapdeal, FreeCharge launch digital wallet Suvidhaa buys AasaanPay’s mobile platform Slamming the rumors of her boob job, Kylie Jenner shared the two pictures, showing off her boobs, to prove that she has not undergone any surgery for it.
The 18-year-old Kylie Jenner took to social media and to her new website to prove that her boobs are real and revealed that she has used Victoria’s secret bra trick to make it large, The Mirror reports.
The ‘Keeping Up with the Kardashians’ star posted two pictures, one showing her boobs in boosting bra and then without it and certainly there was a big difference.
She captioned the picture “watch my little trick on my app/website”.
In a video, the reality star said that she has used the victoria’s secret and it was life changing, adding that effect was like 10 times bigger “no contouring, no nothing”.
Earlier, Jenner flaunted her side boob during a PDA date with boyfriend Tyga at the New York Fashion week.
 15, 2015 5:10 pm
